 AgriPrice is a mobile marketplace for farmers and agricultural buyers. It supports nearby offer discovery, booking and queue tracking, chat, notifications, favorites, payments, reviews, and government price data.
 
+## User roles
+
+- **Buyer** publishes produce purchasing offers, prices, and available queue slots.
+- **Farmer** searches purchasing offers and books a delivery queue.
+
+## Architecture
+
+```text
+HTML / CSS / JavaScript UI
+          |
+     Capacitor 8
+          |
+ Android native plugins
+          |
+   Express REST API
+          |
+Supabase PostgreSQL + Firebase
+```
+
+The Android project is included and verified in this repository. The web layer includes iOS-compatible Capacitor dependencies, but an iOS native project and Xcode build are not included in the current submission.
+
 ## Project structure
 
 - `frontend/` — vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript app packaged with Capacitor.
